data.description: Here is your chance to own this stately colonial home sitting on an acre and a half in Old Bellefonte.  A flat corner lot with beautiful trees and plenty of room to enjoy nature.  This estate has a detached garage and a private courtyard for peace and enjoyment.  The first floor of this home has a large family room with a fireplace, formal living and dining room, gorgeous wood paneled study with a half bath and Florida room makes this home perfect for entertaining as well as family living.  Primary bedroom has a large sitting room as well as 3 other bedrooms on the 2nd level.  3rd floor walk-up attic could be renovated into extra living space but is currently used for extra storage.  Basement has a large bathroom and is partially finished with even more storage.  An invisible dog fence is installed around the perimeter for all furry friends.  This home is conveniently located close to dining shopping and Russell schools.   Call today for your private showing.
